column3: Description
This is an Example
Testing and activation of a new A.T. Field during Christmas Eve with the pilots under pressure to ensure the protection of Tokyo-3
An Angel targets NERV during the holiday season. Pilots must repel the attack while the city celebrates
An Angel attacks during a city-wide festival. Pilots must act fast to protect civilians while keeping the chaos under control
An Angel has taken control of a military outpost. The pilots must engage in a bitter cold battle to take back control and eliminate the threat
The battle with a powerful Angel disrupts Tokyo-3s peace. Pilots must recover vital data from a downed satellite while fighting off the enemy
An Angel attacks in the heart of Tokyo-3 during the winter holidays. The pilots must use their training to neutralize the Angel before it disrupts NERV
An Angel hides among the New Year's celebrations. Pilots must act quickly before it destroys Tokyo-3
During the first hours of the New Year a new Angel launches a surprise attack. Pilots must engage it before the situation worsens
An Angel emerges from a glacier creating an ice storm that affects Tokyo-3. Pilots must battle the Angel while dealing with severe weather conditions
The appearance of an Angel triggers a violent storm. The pilots must fight through treacherous conditions to defeat the Angel before it consumes the city
An Angel manipulates the emotional state of the citizenz causing mass panic. The pilots must restore order while fighting off the threat
Tokyo-3 is attacked during a major power outage. Pilots must navigate the dark city and engage an Angel that is manipulating the electrical grid
A secret mission during the Epiphany holiday. Pilots must infiltrate a SEELE lab to stop a dangerous experiment
A powerful Angel emerges in a frozen region. Pilots must battle it while overcoming the challenges posed by extreme cold and the harsh terrain
The battle with an Angel leads to structural damage in the city. Pilots must hold off the Angel while assisting in rescue operations
An Angel utilizes ice-based attacks to disable the citys defenses. Pilots must engage it while protecting vital infrastructure
The Angel attacks by manipulating the water supply. Pilots must fight in the freezing waters of the Tokyo-3 river while stopping the Angels plans
An Angel makes a strategic move forcing the pilots to confront it in a flooded district. The missions success depends on fast action
An Angel manipulates the freezing temperatures to disable power stations. Pilots must fight through ice storms to prevent a city-wide blackout
An Angel creates a cold zone that affects both human and Eva units. Pilots must fight against time to eliminate the threat
During a brutal snowstorm an Angel attempts to freeze NERVs defenses. Pilots must race against the storm to prevent a catastrophic loss
An Angel hides in a mountain region making it difficult to detect. Pilots must use all available resources to locate and eliminate it
A series of coordinated attacks by Angels leaves the city in a state of chaos. Pilots must restore order while dealing with the harsh winter conditions
An Angel manipulates frozen weapons that can destroy the pilots Evas. The mission becomes a battle of tactical ingenuity to outsmart the enemy
An Angel freezes all mechanical systems in Tokyo-3. Pilots must engage in hand-to-hand combat while trying to restore power
An Angel combines fire and ice-based attacks to overwhelm Tokyo-3s defenses. Pilots must adapt to new combat conditions to survive
An Angels influence causes ice to shatter across the city. Pilots must work together to contain the threat and prevent total destruction
An Angel attacks during the worst snowstorm Tokyo-3 has ever seen. Pilots must track and neutralize it while navigating the blizzard
An Angel feeds off the frozen hearts of the population causing emotional turmoil. Pilots must resist its influence and fight back
An Angel summons an ice storm over the northern region of Tokyo-3. Pilots must fight through blizzards and mountains to defeat it
The final battle against a colossal Angel that has frozen the city. Pilots must prepare for the ultimate confrontation as time runs out
An Angel threatens the last standing power plant. Pilots must eliminate it before the entire city goes dark
An Angel hides in a glacier and manipulates the landscape. Pilots must navigate the dangerous ice caverns to find and destroy it
An Angel manipulates shadows within the citys frozen districts. Pilots must fight against the shifting environment and neutralize the threat
An Angel shatters the infrastructure of Tokyo-3 causing the city to fall into chaos. Pilots must protect key locations while engaging the enemy
An Angels presence causes the Evas to malfunction requiring pilots to rely on their instincts to stop it
The final confrontation with the last of the winter-based Angels. Pilots must overcome all odds to save Tokyo-3 from total destruction
The ultimate battle against an Angel that threatens to encase Tokyo-3 in ice forever. Pilots must give everything to stop the looming catastrophe
